{"tid":737406,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍晉三用中文出tweet多謝台灣幫助","createTime":"2018-07-11T00:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T01:07:55.000Z","uid":51271,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ee0778a4dd447e097810ea70e6e10c2394a0f0","tid":737406,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T00:40:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AbeShinzo/status/1016626757250633728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAbeShinzo%2Fstatus%2F1016626757250633728&d=XmXHZOKFDudAq4yH%2BK1AAaEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=92195644\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAbeShinzo%2Fstatus%2F1016626757250633728&h=5114163d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AbeShinzo/status/1016626757250633728</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安倍晋三<br />\n&rlm;Verified account @AbeShinzo<br />\n<br />\n安倍晋三 Retweeted 蔡英文 Tsai Ing-wen<br />\n<br />\n衷心感謝真心的慰問。已經收到來自台灣各界的關懷協助之意和迅速向災區捐款,對此表示由衷的謝意。<br />\n東日本大地震之際,台灣老朋友們的暖人心懷支援,也令我們都刻骨銘心。<br />\n台灣老朋友不変的友情鼓勵我們復興。<br />\n暴雨和地震等自然災害是我們共同面臨的重大課題。希望今後也同心協力,共渡困難！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f17264b30a3a19624801d25948c6b3c3463e2a3","tid":737406,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T00:41:15.000Z","msg":"而之前蔡英文用日文出tweet:<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文 Tsai Ing-wen<br />\n&rlm;Verified account @iingwen<br />\n<br />\n西日本を中心に発生した豪雨に遭われた日本国民の皆様にお見舞い申し上げます。被害に遭われた方々の回復と被災地の早期復旧をお祈り申し上げます。 <br />\n<br />\n台湾でも豪雨被害は頻発しており、我々もその被害の深刻さを身をもって経験しています。 台湾は日本が必要とするあらゆる支援を行う用意があります。"},{"pid":"c0bf4d1afde402056c791abde65e621358222e17","tid":737406,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T00:41:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1e9f68972b77961ea6513c9b93d4e46ecd094be","tid":737406,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c0bf4d1afde402056c791abde65e621358222e17","tid":737406,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T00:41:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T00:43:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/politicsaeconomy/politicsasociety/30643-2018-06-13-05-00-40.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.cn.nikkei.com%2Fpoliticsaeconomy%2Fpoliticsasociety%2F30643-2018-06-13-05-00-40.html&d=XmXHZOKFDudAq4yH%2BK1AAaEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=0a4cd2f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/politicsaeconomy/politicsasociety/30643-2018-06-13-05-00-40.html</a><br />\n<br />\n安倍是怎麼玩社交媒體的<br />\n<br />\n日本政府正在積極利用社交網站（SNS）展開宣傳。日本首相官邸1月開設了Instagram帳號，並專注於「曬INS」。以日本首相安倍晉三的動向為中心，以圖片直觀地介紹其新年穿和服的身姿、為奧運會加油助威、首腦會談等等。而在擁有約42萬名粉絲的Facebook帳號上，首相官邸則活用視頻，還通過用多種語言發帖等方式在面向海外的宣傳方面下功夫。負責這項工作的是內閣廣報室內部一支被通稱為「SNS班」的團隊。<br />\n<br />\n該團隊總計9人。以20～30多歲的年輕人為中心，部分成員來自民營企業、其他省廳和地方政府等。一般情況下，其中1個人作為攝影人員與安倍同行，拍攝照片和視頻。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n除了攝影人員之外，負責發帖工作的人員為4人，視頻編輯為1人。發帖者採取值班制。他們負責從外出的攝影人員那裏收集照片等材料，使用專用的電腦撰寫當天發帖的文案。"},{"pid":"c09d863b27d4b8cd3cf0401e49589d0ec32b8aff","tid":737406,"uid":133896,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f5ee0778a4dd447e097810ea70e6e10c2394a0f0","tid":737406,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T00:40:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AbeShinzo/status/1016626757250633728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAbeShinzo%2Fstatus%2F1016626757250633728&d=XmXHZOKFDudAq4yH%2BK1AAaEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=92195644\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAbeShinzo%2Fstatus%2F1016626757250633728&h=5114163d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AbeShinzo/status/1016626757250633728</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安倍晋三<br />\n&rlm;Verified account @AbeShinzo<br />\n<br />\n安倍晋三 Retweeted 蔡英文 Tsai Ing-wen<br />\n<br />\n衷心感謝真心的慰問。已經收到來自台灣各界的關懷協助之意和迅速向災區捐款,對此表示由衷的謝意。<br />\n東日本大地震之際,台灣老朋友們的暖人心懷支援,也令我們都刻骨銘心。<br />\n台灣老朋友不変的友情鼓勵我們復興。<br />\n暴雨和地震等自然災害是我們共同面臨的重大課題。希望今後也同心協力,共渡困難！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T00:45:25.000Z","msg":"好似google translate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5948050835665fca849c75a324bb2ae680fd8797","tid":737406,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T01:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}